Part 6: Follow-up Survey, Part B. We may also be interested in recontacting
you at some point after the follow up for an additionally follow-up survey.
These contacts will be made by email and the survey will be administered via an
online questionnaire. You will be contacted by your preferred email and all of
your answers will be kept confidential. Each contact will last no longer than
30 minutes, and you will be compensated at a base rate of $5 and an additional
$0-$13 based on your responses for a total payment of $5-$18. If you consent to agree to participate in this portion of
the study (follow-up contact), please provide your initials below. Otherwise,
you may leave this section blank
